        "id": 1119004
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-04-25T23:38:05Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "If you\u0027re invoking x86_64-cros-linux-gnu-go, armv7a-cros-linux-gnueabi-go, or even the host x86_64-pc-linux-gnu-go from /usr/bin, they\u0027re wrappers that override these GO_* variables. i.e. armv7a-cros-linux-gnueabi-go will cross-compile for arm even if the user has GOARCH set to something else.",
      "parentUuid": "a686c70f_3f711e77",
      "revId": "4493c8196d28d695a1afbbaf49c01f613a854514",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": false
